1 Courtyard South (Start)

Description:
You awaken in the south end of a sunny treed courtyard that surrounds a large 3-storey building.  There are no obvious
exits to the courtyard.  You are surrounded by walls to the south, east, and west but can walk around the building.  
The building has one barred window on the side you can see.  You can hear a bird chirping.  On the ground, there is a 
stone saying “Get to the roof”.
End 

Objects to interact With:
None

Exit Room: W- Courtyard West, E- Courtyard East



2 Courtyard East

Description: 
You are currently in the east end of the courtyard.  There is an empty backpack on the ground with the words “holds
20 objects” stenciled on.
End

Objects to interact With: Backpack (take)

Exit Room: N- Courtyard North, S- Courtyard South

 

3 Courtyard West

Description: 
You are currently in the west end of the courtyard.  There is one tree with a bird nest about 50 feet up.  
The sun is reflecting off something metallic in the nest.  There is a sign saying “The Magic Word is XYZZY”.
End

Objects to interact With: Tree (climb), Key in Nest (take)

Exit Room: N- Courtyard North, S- Courtyard South

 

4 Courtyard North

Description:
You are currently in the north end of the courtyard.  There is a locked door on this side of the building.
End

Objects to interact With: Door (open with key)

Exit Room: W- Courtyard West, E- Courtyard East, South- Hall (through door with key)

 

5 Hall North

Description: 
You are at the north end of a long hall.  Behind you, there is a door leading to the courtyard.  At the end of 
the hallway on the south end, there are two doors and an elevator.
End

Objects to interact With: None

Exit Room: N- Courtyard North, S-Hall South



6 Hall South

Description: 
You are at the south end of a long hall.  There are two doors: one to the east and one to the west.
In front of you, there is an elevator that doesn’t seem to operate due to a lack of electricity.  There
is a sign on the wall saying “Turn on the power to go up”.
End

Objects to interact With: None

Exit Room: N- Hall North, East- Kitchen, West- Library, South- Elevator (with power)


7 Kitchen

Description:
You are in a kitchen.  There is a bag of apples and a butcher knife on the counter and a flashlight.   
End

Objects to interact With: None

Exit Room: West- Hall South



8 Library

Description: 
You are in a library with a dusty bookcase which contains the books “The Life and History of Shon Czinner”, 
“How to Properly Cook a Chicken”, “A History of Hidden Staircases”, and “The Advanced Guide to Having Swag, 
By: Shon Czinner”.
End

Objects to interact With: Each book (take), A History of Hidden Staircases (read: “all hidden staircases are opened by saying the magic word”)

Exit Room: East- Hall South, West- Hidden Staircase (if Magic Word is Said)

 


 
